Bank of the James Financial stock analysis involves checking at least a few of the important things like: Revenue: This is the inflow that is generated from the sale of goods or services and is $6.39M for this quarter of 2017-Q1.  Our Bank of the James Financial revenue chart gives a clear visual representation of how the topline growth has been.  Investors often invest in only those companies where the revenue is growing at a steady rate.  Bottom line: Most businesses like Bank of the James Financial try to improve their bottom line by growing their topline and by increasing their operating efficiency.  A healthy bottom line growth implies a good investment.  The income statement is also called the profit and loss statement.  Apart from the income statement, one can check the Bank of the James Financial historical stock prices to check how the price has moved with time.  . 

